---
import BaseHead from "../components/BaseHead.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from "../consts";
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
		<style>
			.headshot {
				float: right;
			}
			@media (max-width: 720px) {
				.headshot {
					float: none;
				}
			}

			.scaled-image {
				height: 1.5em;
				border-radius: 0px;
				margin-bottom: -0.4em;
			}

			main {
				min-height: 340px;
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<figure class="headshot">
				<img src="img/Anton.jpg" alt="Anton" />
			</figure>
			<p>
				Hi, I'm Anton Geraschenko. I'm a mathematician and software engineer.
				I currently work at <a href="https://plasmidsaurus.com">Plasmidsaurus</a>.
				I've also worked/studied at Google, Eonite Perception, Caltech,
				UC Berkeley, and Brandeis.
			</p>
			<p>
				When I was in academia, my mathematical interests were largely
				in algebraic geometry, particularly foundational questions about
				algebraic stacks. I founded
				<a href="https://mathoverflow.net"><img src="img/MOlogo.svg" alt="MathOverflow" class="scaled-image" /></a>,
				and helped make it successful.
			</p>
			<p>
				More recently I've been interested in probability, information
				theory, and reinforcement learning. Some of my public-facing
				projects include using millions of phones <a
				href="https://www.nature.com/articles/s41586-024-08072-x">to map
				the ionosphere</a> and using differentiable programming and
				monte carlo sampling to <a
				href="https://github.com/verilylifesciences/site-selection-tool">make
				clinical trials faster</a>.
			</p>

			<p>
				If you're looking for my old <a
				href="https://stacky.net/wiki/index.php?title=Course_notes">course
				notes</a> or <a
				href="https://stacky.net/wiki/index.php?title=Category:Blog">blog
				posts</a>, you can find them at my old wiki <a
				href="https://stacky.net">stacky.net</a>. I'll
				probably move most of that stuff here eventually.
			</p>
			<p>
				You can email me at <a
				href="mailto:geraschenko@gmail.com">geraschenko@gmail.com</a>.
			</p>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
